{
  "annotations": { "list": [] },
  "description": "Claude Code usage — cost, tokens, and activity",
  "editable": true,
  "fiscalYearStartMonth": 0,
  "graphTooltip": 1,
  "id": null,
  "links": [],
  "refresh": "5m",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "tags": ["claude-code"],
  "time": { "from": "now-24h", "to": "now" },
  "timepicker": {},
  "timezone": "browser",
  "title": "Claude Code",
  "uid": "claude-code-observability",
  "version": 1,
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Prometheus",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "prometheus",
        "refresh": 1,
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      },
      {
        "current": {},
        "hide": 0,
        "includeAll": false,
        "label": "Loki",
        "multi": false,
        "name": "loki_datasource",
        "options": [],
        "query": "loki",
        "refresh": 1,
        "skipUrlSync": false,
        "type": "datasource"
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 20, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Token types** — `input`: everything sent to the model per turn (history + system prompt + your message), grows as context accumulates · `cacheRead`: tokens served from Anthropic cache at ≈50% cost, should dominate in a healthy session · `output`: model response tokens · `cacheCreation`: new cache entries written this turn, small one-time cost to prime future reads\n\n**Watch for** — Token burn spike → approaching TPM ceiling, start a fresh session · `input` rising toward `cacheRead` → context snowballing, run `/compact` · Cache hit below 80% → cache not reusing effectively · Opus dominating cost → check if Sonnet or Haiku handles the task"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": { "x": 20, "y": 0, "w": 4, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### [Claude Code Logs →](/d/claude-code-logs)\n\nLevel filtering · Session drill-down · Error investigation"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Key Numbers",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 4, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 45,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cost Burn Rate ($/hr)",
      "description": "Real-time cost in dollars per hour based on the last 5 minutes of activity. A spike here means Opus is running or a large context window is in play.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 3,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 2.0 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(rate(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total[5m])) * 3600",
          "legendFormat": "$/hr",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cost Today",
      "description": "Total API spend in the last 24 hours across all sessions and models.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 3, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 10 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 50 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total[24h]))",
          "legendFormat": "Cost Today",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 46,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "7-Day Avg Cost",
      "description": "Rolling average of daily cost over the past 7 days. Compare against Cost Today to see if today is above or below your recent baseline.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "text", "value": null }]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "avg_over_time((sum(increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total[24h])))[7d:24h])",
          "instant": true,
          "legendFormat": "7d Avg",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cost per Session",
      "description": "Average API spend per Claude Code session. Rising cost per session usually means context is snowballing — try /compact to reset.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 9, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 5 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 20 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total[24h])) / clamp_min(sum(increase(claude_code_session_count_total[24h])), 1)",
          "legendFormat": "Cost/Session",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cache Hit Rate",
      "description": "Share of input-side tokens served from cache. Above 80% means you're spending efficiently. Below 60% suggests the context window is growing faster than cache is being reused.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percentunit",
          "decimals": 1,
          "min": 0,
          "max": 1,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.6 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 0.8 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{type=\"cacheRead\"}[24h])) / clamp_min(sum(increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{type=~\"input|cacheRead|cacheCreation\"}[24h])), 1)",
          "legendFormat": "Cache Hit Rate",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tokens Today",
      "description": "All tokens consumed in the last 24 hours across all types: input, output, cacheRead, and cacheCreation.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 15, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "blue", "value": null }]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total[24h]))",
          "legendFormat": "Tokens",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Tokens per Session",
      "description": "Average token consumption per session in the last 24 hours. A rising number over time points to context accumulation across long sessions.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "blue", "value": null }]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total[24h])) / clamp_min(sum(increase(claude_code_session_count_total[24h])), 1)",
          "legendFormat": "Tokens/Session",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Sessions Today",
      "description": "Number of Claude Code sessions in the last 24 hours.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 21, "y": 5, "w": 3, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [{ "color": "blue", "value": null }]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(increase(claude_code_session_count_total[24h]))",
          "legendFormat": "Sessions",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Token Activity [OTEL]",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 9, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Token Burn Rate — All Types Over Time [OTEL]",
      "description": "Token consumption rate broken down by type. cacheRead should dominate a healthy long session. A spike in input without a matching cacheRead rise means context is growing without being cached.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 10, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "right", "calcs": [] }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 1,
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 1,
            "fillOpacity": 20,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (type) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total[10m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Input vs Cache Read — Context Snowball Detector [OTEL]",
      "description": "When input climbs toward or above cacheRead, context is snowballing — the model is processing more new tokens than cached ones each turn. Run /compact to reset before hitting the TPM ceiling.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 8, "y": 10, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "right", "calcs": [] }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 1,
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "stacking": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false }
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "cacheRead" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "blue" } }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "input" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (type) (increase(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{type=~\"input|cacheRead\"}[10m]))",
          "legendFormat": "{{type}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Cost Burn Rate by Model — $/min [OTEL]",
      "description": "Real-time cost per minute broken down by model. Opus appearing here at scale is the most common cause of unexpected bills — check whether Sonnet or Haiku could handle the same task.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 16, "y": 10, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "tooltip": { "mode": "multi", "sort": "desc" },
        "legend": { "displayMode": "list", "placement": "right", "calcs": [] }
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4,
          "color": { "mode": "palette-classic" },
          "custom": {
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "gradientMode": "none",
            "spanNulls": false,
            "showPoints": "auto",
            "pointSize": 4,
            "stacking": { "mode": "none", "group": "A" },
            "axisPlacement": "auto",
            "scaleDistribution": { "type": "linear" },
            "hideFrom": { "legend": false, "tooltip": false, "viz": false }
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (model) (rate(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total[10m]) * 60)",
          "legendFormat": "{{model}}",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "row",
      "title": "Token Breakdown [OTEL]",
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 18, "w": 24, "h": 1 }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Token Volume by Type [OTEL]",
      "description": "Cumulative token counts split by type. cacheRead dwarfing input is a sign of an efficient, well-cached workflow.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 19, "w": 4, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "total_tokens", "desc": true }]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "min": 0,
          "custom": { "align": "auto", "displayMode": "auto" }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "total_tokens" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.displayMode", "value": "gradient-gauge" },
              { "id": "custom.align", "value": "left" }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "type" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 115 }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": { "Value": "total_tokens" }
          }
        }
      ],
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum by (type) (claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total)",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "type": "table",
      "title": "Total Cost by Session — Top 10 [OTEL]",
      "description": "Most expensive sessions in the selected time range. A single session dominating the list usually means a very long context window or heavy Opus usage.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 4, "y": 19, "w": 8, "h": 8 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "showHeader": true,
        "sortBy": [{ "displayName": "cost", "desc": true }]
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "align": "auto", "displayMode": "auto" }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "cost" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "unit", "value": "currencyUSD" },
              { "id": "decimals", "value": 2 },
              { "id": "custom.width", "value": 90 }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      "transformations": [
        {
          "id": "organize",
          "options": {
            "excludeByName": { "Time": true, "__name__": true, "instance": true, "job": true },
            "renameByName": { "Value": "cost" },
            "indexByName": { "Value": 0, "session_id": 1 }
          }
        }
      ],
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "topk(10, sum by (session_id) (claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total))",
          "format": "table",
          "instant": true,
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cost per 1k Output Tokens [OTEL]",
      "description": "Effective cost per 1,000 output tokens across all sessions. Higher than expected means heavy Opus usage or poor cache reuse driving up context costs. Benchmark: Sonnet ≈$0.015, Opus ≈$0.075.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 19, "w": 8, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "currencyUSD",
          "decimals": 4,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.02 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.06 }
            ]
          },
          "mappings": []
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
          "expr": "sum(claude_code_cost_usage_USD_total) / sum(claude_code_token_usage_tokens_total{type=\"output\"}) * 1000",
          "legendFormat": "",
          "refId": "A",
          "instant": true
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Cache Reuse Ratio [OTEL]",
      "description": "cacheRead tokens divided by cacheCreation tokens. How many times each cached block is being reused on average. Above 5 is good — cache is paying for itself. Below 2 means you're writing cache entries that rarely get reused.",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 23, "w": 8, "h": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "${datasource}" },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "values": false, "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "" },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "auto",
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center"
      },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 1,
          "color": { "mode": "thresholds" },
          "thresholds": {
